Package metrix.size

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NoEHExtractor
    Number of Empty Handlers: The number of empty handlers (i.e., catch blocs) in a given class.
    NoGHExtractor
    Number of General Handlers: The number of general handlers in a given class (i.e., the catch blocks that catches java.lang.Exception or java.lang.Throwable).
    NoHExtractor
    Number of Handling: The number of exception handled by a given class divided by a number of methods and constructors of this class.
    NoRExtractor
    Number of Raising: The number of exception raised by a given class divided by a number of methods and constructors of this class.
    NoSExtractor
    Number of Signaling: The number of exception signaled by a given class divided by a number of methods and constructors of this class.
